{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "$id": "https://example.com/friends-schema.json",
  "title": "Friends Data Schema",
  "description": "Schema for validating friends data",
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "friends": {
      "type": "array",
      "description": "Array of friend objects",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "name": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Friend's name",
            "minLength": 1,
            "maxLength": 50
          },
          "age": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "Friend's age",
            "minimum": 0,
            "maximum": 150
          }
        },
        "required": ["name", "age"],
        "additionalProperties": false
      }
    }
  },
  "required": ["friends"],
  "additionalProperties": false
}


Common JSON Schema Keywords
Keyword	Purpose	Example
type	Data type	"type": "string"
required	Required fields	"required": ["name", "age"]
properties	Object properties	Defines structure
minLength/maxLength	String length	"minLength": 1
minimum/maximum	Number range	"minimum": 0
pattern	Regex pattern	"pattern": "^[A-Za-z]+$"
format	Data format	"format": "email"
items	Array items schema	Defines array elements
additionalProperties	Allow extra props	false to restrict